Data availability

            All data presented in this work were generated from model experiments using the open-source Parallel Ice Sheet Model (https://github.com/pism/pism/). Model outputs presented in this paper are available online at https://osf.io/wbne9/overview.
          Code availability

            Julia and GMT scripts used to calculate the Shannon entropy and to plot all of the figures are available at https://osf.io/wbne9/overview. However, most of the analyses presented in the paper are easily achieved using data-processing software such as Generic Mapping Tools (GMT), Python, Julia or Matlab.
